OL,3,CEnergy watchdog steps in as supplier
OL,4,Ccollapses impacting 24,000 customers
OL,6,FBasingstoke-based supplier, Tomato
OL,7,FEnergy, has collapsed, leaving the
OL,8,Findustry watchdog to step in to
OL,9,Fprotect supply for the provider's
OL,10,F15,300 household and 8,400 business
OL,11,Fcustomers.
OL,13,FRegulator Ofgem said energy supply and
OL,14,Ffunds paid into accounts, including
OL,15,Fcredit balances, will be secured for
OL,16,FTomato Energy's customers under the
OL,17,Fsupplier of last resort safety net.
