OL,3,CEnergy watchdog steps in as supplier
OL,4,Ccollapses impacting 24,000 customers
OL,6,FCustomers of Tomato Energy are being
OL,7,Fadvised not to switch as they will be
OL,8,Fcontacted by their new supplier, which
OL,9,Fwill be allocated by Ofgem in the
OL,10,Fcoming days.
OL,12,FThey are advised to take a meter
OL,13,Freading before they are contacted by
OL,14,Ftheir new supplier.
OL,16,FOfgem said household customers would
OL,17,Falso continue to be protected by the
OL,18,Fenergy cap when switching to the new
OL,19,Fsupplier.
