OL,3,CEnergy watchdog steps in as supplier
OL,4,Ccollapses impacting 24,000 customers
OL,6,FIt is understood the company, which
OL,7,Femploys around 100 people, will
OL,8,Fformally appoint administrators in the
OL,9,Fcoming days.
OL,11,FTomato Energy was banned from taking
OL,12,Fon new customers in April after
OL,13,Fbuilding up debts of #3 million.
OL,15,FIt was then hit with a proposed #1.5
OL,16,Fmillion fine from Ofgem last month for
OL,17,Ffailing to meet financial resilience
OL,18,Frules and the firm filed a notice of
OL,19,Fintent to appoint administrators at
OL,20,Fthe end of October.
