OL,3,CEnergy watchdog steps in as supplier
OL,4,Ccollapses impacting 24,000 customers
OL,6,FRohan Churm, director for financial
OL,7,Fresilience and control, said: "I want
OL,8,Fto reassure Tomato Energy customers
OL,9,Fthat they do not need to worry.
OL,11,F"They will not see any disruption to
OL,12,Ftheir energy supply, and any credit
OL,13,Fdomestic customers have on their
OL,14,Faccounts remains protected under
OL,15,FOfgem's rules.
OL,17,F"We are working quickly to appoint a
OL,18,Fnew supplier for all existing
OL,19,Fcustomers, and they should not switch
OL,20,Fin the meantime."
