OL,3,CEnergy watchdog steps in as supplier
OL,4,Ccollapses impacting 24,000 customers
OL,6,FOnce they have been contacted by their
OL,7,Fnew supplier, customers can ask to be
OL,8,Fput on the cheapest deal or look for
OL,9,Fan alternative deal from another
OL,10,Fsupplier.
OL,12,FThey will not be charged exit fees for
OL,13,Fswitching away from their new supplier.
OL,15,FOfgem said suppliers must now have
OL,16,Fcapital to cover their risks and ring-
OL,17,Ffence certain areas of their finances
OL,18,Fsuch as customer credit balances under
OL,19,Fnew rules.
