OL,3,CEnergy watchdog steps in as supplier
OL,4,Ccollapses impacting 24,000 customers
OL,6,FMr Churm added: "We have worked hard
OL,7,Fto improve the financial resilience of
OL,8,Fsuppliers in recent years,
OL,9,Fimplementing a series of rules to make
OL,10,Fsure they can weather unexpected
OL,11,Fshocks.
OL,13,F"But like any competitive market, some
OL,14,Fcompanies will still fail from time to
OL,15,Ftime and our priority is making sure
OL,16,Fconsumers are protected if that
OL,17,Fhappens and that any associated costs
OL,18,Fare minimised."
